{"tid":1761550,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"趕屯門公園大媽方法","createTime":"2019-11-29T03:54:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-09T12:17:11.000Z","uid":283164,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"2bd36762de31cf63ae39a64ed601aed7bece8aef","tid":1761550,"uid":283164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T03:54:20.000Z","msg":"當你見到屯公大媽唱歌嘅時候有兩個方法<br />\n<br />\n1.向在場保安投訴（記得要發老脾）<br />\n       跟住保安就會指你去康文個office,保安係呢個時候就會用對講機，叫其他保安叫大媽收檔。<br />\n       當你去到office 到，場地主任就會問你<br />\n         <span style=\"font-size: large;\">「係咪要做証人」</span>答係<br />\n       如果你話有片有相係唔得嘅，一定要康文處人員做証人。呢個時候，康文嘅人就會叫你同佢一齊睇邊到有滋擾。<br />\n       當然你係投訴唔到人嘅，因為場地保安已經清左大媽走。<br />\n<br />\n2. 正式立案投訴<br />\n     只要你見到大媽唱歌，不動聲色咁去到康文office話，要投訴。<br />\n     佢就會跟你去到現場，邊到俾大媽滋擾。<br />\n成功嘅就會立案排期上庭。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WmBdDW8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWmBdDW8.jpg&h=b5b860dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n屯門康文office 係爬蟲館對面，何日東後面"},{"pid":"171c4d11ced277456e3a7ab43c4d11d3b007296a","tid":1761550,"uid":256246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T03:55:28.000Z","msg":"幫襯完唔俾錢"},{"pid":"2b6561cad44205976fefa84ca6e3ba02378a10c2","tid":1761550,"uid":149559,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T04:05:01.000Z","msg":"而家多左個 option 區議員 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da1198a5496ea5bb017accdd6ccb9d519c1d3069","tid":1761550,"uid":8812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T04:07:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"102cebc5e88bd5d7861b999db017fca02eeffcb2","tid":1761550,"uid":180536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T08:30:48.000Z","msg":"提提大家  要投訴大媽躁音問題記得揾著黑衫保安投訴，佢哋先係管理躁音問題架 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但係黑衫個啲全部係退休紀律部隊，有啲仲係狗黎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n平時都唔理大媽躁音，自己都聽埋一份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a30218c457ee441b48551499ea51949f6bd85695","tid":1761550,"uid":283164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"102cebc5e88bd5d7861b999db017fca02eeffcb2","tid":1761550,"uid":180536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T08:30:48.000Z","msg":"提提大家  要投訴大媽躁音問題記得揾著黑衫保安投訴，佢哋先係管理躁音問題架 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但係黑衫個啲全部係退休紀律部隊，有啲仲係狗黎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n平時都唔理大媽躁音，自己都聽埋一份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T12:17:11.000Z","msg":"多謝提醒"}]}